text: private ITrendChartControl GetChartControl(IInspectionItemResult itemResult) { if (itemResult is null) return null; switch (resultProvider.GetItemType(itemResult)) { case ItemType.Coating: case ItemType.NonCoating: 1{ return trendChartControls[TrendChartType.HistogramTrend].Value; } case ItemType.ICComponent: 1{ return trendChartControls[TrendChartType.ThicknessTrend].Value; } case ItemType.Underfill: 1{ if (itemResult.MeasureType == MeasureType.UnderfillOverfill || itemResult.MeasureType == MeasureType.UnderfillOffset) return null; return trendChartControls[TrendChartType.PivotTrend].Value; } default: 1{ return null; } } }
